description:
Gundam Breaker 4 is an action hack-and-slash RPG Gundam game developed by Crafts & Meister Co. Players can customize and use their very own Gundams against others in third-person combat using various abilities and weapons. A new collaboration for the game has been announced bringing a special PAC-MAN level complete with themed enemies, and unlockable decals to use in the rest of the game. Check out the trailer to see a glimpse of the Gundam Breaker 4 x Pac-Man collaboration for Gundam Breaker 4, launching on August 28 for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Nintendo Switch, and PC (Steam).

description:
Bleach Rebirth of Souls is a 3D fighting game developed by Tamsoft Corporation. Players will embody a wide variety of characters from the iconic anime series and wield powerful sword abilities in intense combat. Unlock new forms and new blades as players progress throughout the game and reign victorious when the dust has settled. Bleach Rebirth of Souls is launching soon for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).
